Name: cs_limitsetfounder
Author: oldAuthors
Category: ChanServ
Last updated: 2006-12-24T21:44:59+00:00

Limits the use of /msg ChanServ SET #channel FOUNDER to one of three user levels:

 - Services Roots only
 - Services Admins and above
 - Services Opers and above

The module has one configuration directive which [b]needs[/b] to be placed into services.conf before the module is loaded:

# LimitCSSetFounder &lt;level&gt; [REQUIRED]
#     Limits the user of /msg ChanServ SET #channel FOUNDER
#     to the user level specified below.
#
#     For services roots only, use "root".
#     For services admins and above, use "admin".
#     For services opers and above, use "oper".
LimitCSSetFounder "root"

Version 1.0.0 supports Anope 1.7.16
Version 1.0.1 supports Anope 1.7.16
